### Sets API
### CRUD operations for user's LEGO sets collection

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/sets
@token = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### List Sets
# Returns paginated sets for authenticated user
# Supports filtering by search, theme, tags, isBuilt
# Supports sorting by title, setNumber, pieceCount, purchaseDate, purchasePrice, createdAt
# http://localhost:3000/api/sets/list
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sets/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List Sets with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}search=millennium&theme=Star Wars&isBuilt=true&sortField=title&sortDirection=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Set by ID
# @name getSet
@setId = ee007dfd-e170-401f-a9c1-4c3983e8bdfb

GET {{baseUrl}}/{{setId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Set
# Creates a new set for the authenticated user

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Millennium Falcon",
  "setNumber": "75192",
  "store": "LEGO",
  "pieceCount": 7541,
  "theme": "Star Wars",
  "tags": ["UCS", "Star Wars", "Display"],
  "isBuilt": false,
  "quantity": 1,
  "purchasePrice": 849.99,
  "notes": "Ultimate Collector Series"
}

###

